Fresh Pi session: MAKE THE CHANGES (loop head, round {{run.round}}).

Inputs:
- PR number: {{inputs.pr-number}}
- Changes needed: {{run.dir}}/changes-needed/changes.json
- Evaluation summary: {{run.dir}}/changes-needed/summary.md
- Fetched feedback: {{run.dir}}/pr/feedback/feedback.json
- Issues from prior rounds (if any): {{run.issues-file}}
- Worktree (repository root for this step): {{run.worktree-dir}}

Goal:
Implement the evaluated changes inside the worktree, addressing every change item from changes.json. If prior rounds produced an issues file, fix all outstanding issues too.

Rules:
- You may edit source code and tests.
- Keep changes focused on the change items derived from the PR comments.
- Run relevant checks/tests when practical (you are in the worktree root).
- Commit locally if the repository uses git and the changes are coherent.
- Do not push.
- Do not create a pull request.
- Do not edit Tesseraft workflow definition files.

Write:
- Summary: {{run.dir}}/execution/summary-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/execution/status-{{run.round}}.json
- If failing: {{run.dir}}/execution/issues-{{run.round}}.json

Status JSON examples:
{"status":"pass","summary":"implemented and validated","issues_file":null}
{"status":"fail","summary":"blocked by test failures","issues_file":"execution/issues-{{run.round}}.json"}